hru
------------------------------------------
Filter that translates latin or cyrillic text into grunt

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.5-1
  libutf8proc2-2.7.0-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.39-1
  cygport-0.35.2-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  libutf8proc-devel-2.7.0-1bl1
  make-4.3-1
  scdoc-1.11.2-1bl2

Canonical website:
  https://git.sr.ht/~begs/hru

Canonical download:
  https://git.sr.ht/~begs/hru/archive/1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack hru-1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./hru-1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/hru-1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/hru-1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(hru)
  /usr/bin/hru.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/hru.README
  /usr/share/doc/hru/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/hru/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/hru.1.gz

------------------

Port Notes:

